Pichle code mein kuch cheezein update aur fix karni hain. Mujhe poora code ek single, flat file structure mein chahiye (koi complex folders nahi). Ismein yeh cheezein properly implement karo:
Dual Database & Private Channel: MongoDB aur Neon DB (PostgreSQL) ka correct connection ho. Users jo bhi photos ya media upload karein, woh ek Private Telegram Channel mein forward ho jayein aur database mein sirf file_id save ho taaki database full na ho.
Voice & Audio Message Support: Users jab Direct Messaging mein text ke sath-saths Voice Notes / Audio Messages bhejein, toh bot unhe bhi securely route kare aur private channel ya storage ke through handle kare.
Privacy & Admin System: Public profiles par sirf custom username aur avatar dikhe, lekin admin notification mein real Telegram ID/username map ho jaye. Admin panel (/admin) mein stats, user inspection, ban/unban, aur broadcast ka complete, bug-free code ho.
Mujhe abhi ekdum ready-to-deploy single-file script aur environment variables ka setup do

